reviewText: All good movies, love Hilary Swank.

Based on a true story, Freedom is a story brings out the best in what otherwise would have been a class of Black, Latino and Oriental losers.  Swank's portrayal of the teacher, Erin Gruwell was outstanding.  This is a must-see movie.

Some of the films in this collection I had not heard of nor seen before and was very pleasantly surprised, even thrilled after viewing each one. A very nice assortment of thrillers and rom-coms, with great performances to enjoy.
I purchased this because Freedom Writers is such an inspiring movie and I wanted to show it to students. The extra movies were simply a bonus! Great product and fast delivery. Highly recommended!
Excellent movie.  Wanted to see it after hearing the author Erin Gruwell speak at a luncheon in Rochester, MN.
Great Purchase to go with my collection.
I used (Freedom Writers) in my classes to anhance  the knowledge of my students about "what is freedom".
Freedom Writers is such a great movie!  There should be a copy in every library, school library, and copies distributed to teachers everywhere!  What a story!  What a great teacher!
